
======================================
  YouTube Downloader 0.1 by Ronnie-A
======================================


About
-----

  This is a very simple tool to download videos from YouTube.


Dependencies
------------

  YouTube Downloader depends on bash, coreutils, grep, sed and wget.


Usage
-----

  To use YouTube Downloader, type

    $ youtube LINK [FORMAT]

in your console. LINK is a link to YouTube video (for example, http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ) and FORMAT is a video format or quality (for example, 720, 360). If FORMAT is not specified, the best available format will be downloaded.


Feedback
--------

  If you have any comments of suggestions, please send them to ronnie-mail@yandex.ru or pull a request to https://github.com/Ronnie-A/YouTube-Downloader/pulls.